{
  "bio": [
    "Zuo Yuyu is founder and chairman of Leader Harmonious Drive Systems, which makes harmonic reducers - the \"joints\" of robots.",
    "Known also as Leaderdrive, the Suzhou-based company is China's largest manufacturer of harmonic reducers by market cap, with customers such as domestic humanoid company UBTech Robotics.",
    "In February 2026, Leaderdrive agreed to set up a joint venture with Taiwan's auto-parts supplier Minth Group in the U.S. to develop joint modules for humanoids.",
    "Yuyu founded Leaderdrive in 2011 with the aim of making more affordable robotics components.",
    "His brother Jing serves as Leaderdrive's vice chairman."
